    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Occur dAlene theater was\nplaced on the fair list last night\nby the Spokane Trades Council, at\nleast so it was reported this morn\ning This ends the fight which has\nbeen made for several months by\nthe stage employers union against\nthe house, and which at one time\ninvolved the musicians union also."
    }
